statement: WITH pet_food_buyers AS ( SELECT DISTINCT USER_ID FROM rocketview_v4 WHERE (CATEGORY_3 = 'Dog Food' OR CATEGORY_3 = 'Cat Food')), non_pet_food_cpg_brands AS ( SELECT BRAND, SUM(FINAL_SALE) AS sales FROM rocketview_v4 WHERE USER_ID IN (SELECT USER_ID FROM pet_food_buyers) AND CATEGORY_1 != 'Animals & Pet Supplies' AND BRAND IS NOT NULL AND BRAND != 'Empty Fetch Taxonomy BRAND' AND (PL_FLAG IS NULL OR PL_FLAG = false) AND MANUFACTURER IS NOT NULL AND MANUFACTURER NOT IN ('WALMART','COSTCO','SAM''S CLUB','KROGER','ALBERTSONS','TARGET','BJ''S','WINCO FOODS','H-E-B','MEIJER','WEGMANS','SPROUTS','ALDI','TRADER JOE''S','PUBLIX','SAFEWAY','GROCERY OUTLET','FAMILY DOLLAR','DOLLAR GENERAL','DOLLAR TREE','FRESH THYME','GIANT EAGLE','HARRIS TEETER','HY-VEE','INGLES','KING SOOPERS','RALPHS','SMITHS','STOP & SHOP','WHOLE FOODS','FOOD LION','FOOD 4 LESS','FOODS CO','FRED MEYER','FRY''S','HANNAFORD','HARMONS','HARRIS TEETER','JEWEL-OSCO','LIDL','LOWES FOODS','LUCKY','MARC''S','MARTIN''S','PIGGLY WIGGLY','PRICE CHOPPER','QFC','RANDALLS','SAVE A LOT','SCHNUCKS','SHOPRITE','STATER BROS','SUPERVALU','THRIFTWAY','TOM THUMB','VONS','WALGREENS','WALMART','WHOLE FOODS','WINN-DIXIE') GROUP BY BRAND ) SELECT BRAND, sales FROM non_pet_food_cpg_brands ORDER BY sales DESC LIMIT 10

CREATE TABLE `rocketview_v4` (

  `YEAR_PURCHASE` datetime NULL COMMENT "",
  `STORE_NAME` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `RETAILER_BANNER` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `RETAILER_CHANNEL` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `RETAILER_PARENT_COMPANY` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",

  `FIDO` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",

  `MANUFACTURER` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `CATEGORY_1` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `CATEGORY_2` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `CATEGORY_3` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `CATEGORY_4` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `DESCRIPTION` varchar(1048576) NULL COMMENT "",
  `PL_FLAG` boolean NULL COMMENT "",
  `RECEIPT_DIGITAL` boolean NULL COMMENT "",
  `FINAL_QUANTITY` decimal(10, 2) NULL COMMENT "",
  `FINAL_SALE` decimal(10, 2) NULL COMMENT "",
  `IN_HUGGIES_CLUB` boolean NULL COMMENT "",
  `IN_PEPSICO_CLUB` boolean NULL COMMENT "",
  `IN_GENERALMILLS_CLUB` boolean NULL COMMENT "",

DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`USER_ID`) BUCKETS 12

"bloom_filter_columns" = "BRAND, CATEGORY_1, CATEGORY_2, CATEGORY_3, DESCRIPTION, MANUFACTURER, RETAILER_BANNER, STORE_NAME",
"colocate_with" = "rocketview_v4_receipt360_v4",

"replication_num" = "1");
